lead_paragraph: Australia ripped through South Africa's top order in the first hour, dismissed the tourists for 242 by tea and reached 105 without loss at close on the back of some Dave Warner fireworks on the opening day of the first test on Thursday.

headline.print_headline: Australia Dominate Opening Day in Perth
headline.main: Australia Dominate Opening Day in Perth
